    "You have not accessed your files with any client (desktop or mobile) yet. Configure clients on your devices to access your data more comfortably.": "Hen\u00fcz dosyalar\u0131n\u0131za herhangi bir istemci (masa\u00fcst\u00fc veya mobil) ile eri\u015fmediniz. Verilerinize daha rahat eri\u015fmek i\u00e7in cihazlar\u0131n\u0131zdaki istemcileri yap\u0131land\u0131r\u0131n.",
    "You have not added any libraries, folders or files to your favorites yet. A favorite gives you quick access to your most frequently used objects. You can add a library, folder or file to your favorites by clicking the star to the left of its name.": "Hen\u00fcz hi\u00e7bir k\u00fct\u00fcphane, klas\u00f6r veya dosyay\u0131 favorilerinize eklemediniz. Bir favori, en s\u0131k kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z nesnelere h\u0131zl\u0131 eri\u015fim sa\u011flar. Bir k\u00fct\u00fcphane, klas\u00f6r veya dosyay\u0131 favorilerinize eklemek i\u00e7in ad\u0131n\u0131n solundaki y\u0131ld\u0131z simgesine t\u0131klayabilirsiniz.",
    "You have not created any libraries yet. A library is a container to organize your files and folders. A library can also be shared with others and synced to your connected devices. You can create a library by clicking the \"New Library\" item in the dropdown menu.": "Hen\u00fcz hi\u00e7 k\u00fct\u00fcphane olu\u015fturmad\u0131n\u0131z. Bir k\u00fct\u00fcphane, dosya ve klas\u00f6rlerinizi d\u00fczenlemek i\u00e7in bir kapsay\u0131c\u0131d\u0131r. Bir k\u00fct\u00fcphane ba\u015fkalar\u0131yla payla\u015f\u0131labilir ve ba\u011fl\u0131 cihazlar\u0131n\u0131zla senkronize edilebilir. A\u00e7\u0131l\u0131r men\u00fcdeki \"Yeni K\u00fct\u00fcphane\" \u00f6\u011fesine t\u0131klayarak bir k\u00fct\u00fcphane olu\u015fturabilirsiniz.",
    "You have not created any share links yet. A share link can be used to share files and folders with anyone. You can create a share link for a file or folder by clicking the share icon to the right of its name.": "Hen\u00fcz hi\u00e7 payla\u015f\u0131m ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131 olu\u015fturmad\u0131n\u0131z. Bir payla\u015f\u0131m ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131, dosya ve klas\u00f6rleri herkesle payla\u015fmak i\u00e7in kullan\u0131labilir. Bir dosya veya klas\u00f6r i\u00e7in payla\u015f\u0131m ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131 olu\u015fturmak i\u00e7in ad\u0131n\u0131n sa\u011f\u0131ndaki payla\u015f\u0131m simgesine t\u0131klayabilirsiniz.",
    "You have not created any upload links yet. An upload link allows anyone to upload files to a folder or library. You can create an upload link for a folder or library by clicking the share icon to the right of its name.": "Hen\u00fcz hi\u00e7 y\u00fckleme ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131 olu\u015fturmad\u0131n\u0131z. Bir y\u00fckleme ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131, herkesin bir klas\u00f6re veya k\u00fct\u00fcphaneye dosya y\u00fcklemesine izin verir. Bir klas\u00f6r veya k\u00fct\u00fcphane i\u00e7in y\u00fckleme ba\u011flant\u0131s\u0131 olu\u015fturmak i\u00e7in ad\u0131n\u0131n sa\u011f\u0131ndaki payla\u015f\u0131m simgesine t\u0131klayabilirsiniz.",
    "You have not deleted any libraries in the last {placeholder} days. A deleted library will be cleaned automatically after this period.": "Son {placeholder} g\u00fcn i\u00e7inde herhangi bir k\u00fct\u00fcphane silmediniz. Silinen bir k\u00fct\u00fcphane bu s\u00fcreden sonra otomatik olarak temizlenecektir.",
    "You have not invited any guests yet. A guest can access shared libraries through the web interface allowing more efficient ways to collaborate than through links. You can invite a guest by clicking the \"Invite Guest\" item in the dropdown menu.": "Hen\u00fcz hi\u00e7 misafir davet etmediniz. Bir misafir, ba\u011flant\u0131lar yerine web aray\u00fcz\u00fc \u00fczerinden payla\u015f\u0131lan k\u00fct\u00fcphanelere eri\u015febilir ve daha verimli i\u015fbirli\u011fi yap\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 sa\u011flar. A\u00e7\u0131l\u0131r men\u00fcdeki \"Misafir Davet Et\" \u00f6\u011fesine t\u0131klayarak bir misafir davet edebilirsiniz.",
